<td class="mbox-text" style="">It has been suggested that <i><a href="/wiki/Fads_and_trends" title="Fads and trends">Fads and trends</a></i> be <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Merging_and_moving_pages" title="Wikipedia:Merging and moving pages" class="mw-redirect">merged</a> into this article or section. (<a href="/wiki/Talk:Bandwagon_effect#Merge_Fads_and_trends_with_Bandwagon_effect.3F" title="Talk:Bandwagon effect">Discuss</a>)</td>
